### NAAS — Contributions API manual tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json
@token = PASTE_JWT_HERE
@groupId = PASTE_GROUP_ID_HERE
@contributionId = PASTE_CONTRIBUTION_ID_HERE

### ──── List all contributions (current cycle) ───────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/contributions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ──── My contribution status ───────────────────────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/contributions/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ──── Record cash payment (Treasurer) ─────────────────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/contributions/cash
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "memberId": "PASTE_MEMBER_USER_ID",
  "amount": 10000,
  "note": "Paid in cash at meeting"
}

### ──── Retry failed MoMo deduction (Treasurer) ─────────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/contributions/{{contributionId}}/retry
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
